          <p>Underpaid and overeducated is a common theme for my generation. Countless number of people just like myself are sitting around wondering what to do with themselves after they've given their last dollar to the almight gods of higher education and are now simply left holding a bill. </p>

          <p>No job. No girlfriend. No progress. No leads. Not even a clear skill set. A 
